snippet.title: Roblox: Sonic Speed Simulator - Tuxedo Classic Sonic Announcement Trailer | Sonic Central 2023
snippet.description:
Celebrate Sonic's birthday with a new event that unlocks Tuxedo Classic Sonic, the first alternate skin for Classic Sonic in Sonic Speed Simulator on Roblox. Check out some short gameplay, shown during Sonic Central 2023. This new content is available now.

#IGN #SonicTheHedgehog
